facturing mining distribution and service companies ranging from steel processing to internet technologies as well as financial institutions and investment banks serving those industries mr porter was named in  as one of the preeminent lawyers in the united states by the best lawyers in america and has been listed in their publication as a best lawyer in corporate law corporate governance and compliance law mergers  acquisitions law and securities law since  he was named one of the top five securities lawyers in the state of texas by texas lawyer in  and as a texas super lawyer in surveys conducted by texas monthly since  mr porter has been named in super lawyers corporate counsel edition in the area of securities and corporate finance since  in  corporate counsel magazine named him as a best lawyer in corporate law he has been listed in whos who in america and several other whos who publications including whos who in american law since representative experience more than  primary secondary and followon public offerings either as issuer or underwriter counsel more than  merger acquisition and reorganization transactions as counsel for acquirors sellers bankers or principal stockholders board representation covering a broad spectrum of corporate governance issues prosecution and defense of tender offers proxy contests and other change of control transactions goingprivate transactions substantive law advice in connection with securities and corporate litigation matters and administrative proceedings before the securities and exchange commission professional  civic affiliations martindale hubbell av rated attorney served on state bar of texas committees on securities and investment banking corporate law tender offer regulation securities legislation and corporate legal opinions several of which he chaired served on american bar association committees on securities law proxy regulation and law firms trustee texas heart institute   present director alley theatre houston 